Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.45,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:12.79,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:12.79,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.72,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.72,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.16,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.16,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.50,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.50,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.84,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.84,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:11.32,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:11.32,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:51.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought for sure that I heard a faint voice calling my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:09.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wake up in the morning to find a guy sleeping next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:11.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:13.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My youth is way too depressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:18.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that I've hit rock bottom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:23.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:26.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving for work already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:28.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me, you can chill in here for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:33.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please leave the key in the usual place,\Nand don't forget to turn off the AC.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:35.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you working late again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:36.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can come in on your own and cool off if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:41.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even thought it's just a simple morning conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:56.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does the simple fact that I'm having that conversation\Nwith a guy make things so depressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:02.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end, it's just Takemoto and\Nme that are left in the apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:08.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you open it up over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:15.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:16.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasegawa-senpai's homemade soba sure is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:28.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's really working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:31.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he was depressed when he couldn't find a job...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:35.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's prospered ever since he decided\Nto carry on his family's business.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.99,0:03:43.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised. He's already in travel brochures\Nand guidebooks for Shizuoka.
