Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:17.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's Megumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasegawa-san's certainly working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do my best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:33.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as her father, I also want Ayu to inherit my store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:41.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her brother Susumu is incredibly knowledgeable, bus he's\Na little too fond of sake, and isn't quite fit for business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving you away to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:44.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, Ayu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:47.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My first grandchild was finally born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:49.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're about to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Grandpa Tanabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you have no other choice than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:59.28,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz11\fs55\fnArtificeSSK\fscx70\fsp1\shad0\bord2\move(520,459,520,463)\frx350\fry358\c&H3D4348&\3c&HC8D6D7&}Hatsumago
