Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:59.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I prefer one over the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:02.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If we could combine the good in those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:09.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we might be able to become a store so fun\Nthat we could beat even the big discount stores.
