Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what is it, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I already accompanied you on your walk this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:24.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H2C94E4&\pos(434,368)}"Well then, what about breakfast?"
