Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really filled me with depressing feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:34.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that is depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a single bit of romanticism in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:39.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What is it, Mayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you dreaming about your ex-girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:44.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:48.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't anything between us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be that she actually wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mayama-kun, did you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:58.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that when someone appears in your dreams like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:03.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because that other person's desire to see you leaves\Ntheir body and comes flying into your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:12.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so occult. There's no way such a thing could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:14.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a superstition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.53,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is interesting...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're all ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:22.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:25.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your forehead, Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:30.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya-san... No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting injured before the battle? What an ill-fated guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a huge boost if we can get this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's approach it with spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:40.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:49.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\fnTimes New Roman\fs55\shad0\pos(425,446)\c&HE0E1DF&}Meeting in progress
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:52.27,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\fnTimes New Roman\fs55\shad0\pos(425,446)\c&HE0E1DF&}Meeting complete
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:07:03.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Negotiation passed, will return with chicken-breast jerky\Nfor Leader and beer for everyone on the team."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They did it! That's our Nomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the wind feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:14.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The negative ions in the air after a successful\Nnegotiation really feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:16.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The beer will feel even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Shall we go for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go make a toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:24.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:29.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right with not even greeting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:31.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:37.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense beer around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty, why don't we go in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:41.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as if I forgot something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:50.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it was around the fountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:53.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:57.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:07:59.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoom in. Zoom in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Mayama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please start on the beer without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:23.94,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}tsuyogaru poozu ga yoku niteta futari wa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:23.94,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Acting tough, tough we were really alike,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I met her in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:29.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought for sure that I heard a faint voice calling my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:32.79,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}hajikiai sono ato hikiatta
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:32.79,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}we pushed each other away but then were pulled back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:41.29,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}umareta koro to kawaranai kokoro de
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:41.29,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With a heart unchanged since I was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.67,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mayama-kun, did you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:42.55,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that when someone appears in your dreams like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:47.97,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because that other person's desire to see you leaves\Ntheir body and comes flying into your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:56.18,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}sawattara subete ga kiesou na kimi wo mitsumeteita
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:56.18,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've been looking at you, too fragile to touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that could be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:11.74,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}yagate kimi wa tori ni naru boroboro no yakusoku mune ni daite
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:11.74,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Soon you'll become a bird, keeping the crumbling promise in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:02.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I getting all excited for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:10.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How long can you remember a voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:15.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You become worried, and replay it\Nin your head over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:23.46,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kanashii koto mo aru dakedo yume wa tsuzuku me wo fusenaide
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:23.46,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There will be sorrows, but the dream goes on, so keep looking ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can remember it. I can still remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what if...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never meet her again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:32.76,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}maioriru yoake made
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:32.76,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Until the dawn comes dancing down upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:30.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will her figure be the thing that remains until the very end?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:35.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be her voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:45.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so close to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't lick me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already, Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:02.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(434,331)\c&H3D99DD&}"Miwako-san told me that she'd give me food if I woke you up."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:07.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Takemoto-kun a boy that lives in the\Nsame apartment complex as him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:10.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I hadn't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So Mayama-kun was like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:17.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hear me out, please, Miwako-san, Yamazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:21.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sorry about that. It's okay. Don't mind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:22.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:26.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys. Don't tease him so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:28.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider things like that a matter of personal freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:38.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty common in our industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:40.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you, Nomiya-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please print out twenty copies of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:47.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the model needs to be finished by 4:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure wakes me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Messing with Mayama is so refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:59.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You insensitive pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:04.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell on you to our mama in Tottori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:06.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:07.82,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-69\c&H413C38&\fs22\fscx70\3c&HCCC9C5&\bord2\shad0\pos(227,63)\frx12\fry58}President's Office B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:07.82,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz70\c&H413C38&\fs22\fscx70\3c&HCCC9C5&\bord2\shad0\pos(624,60)\frx12\fry302}President's Office A
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:07.82,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H413C38&\fs16\3c&HCCC9C5&\bord2\shad0\frx26\fry354\pos(422,200)}Meeting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:07.82,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\bord0.2\shad1\be1\fs28\frz-41\4c&H4B4F3E&\c&H7D6057&\pos(111,246)\frx4\fry32\3c&H342F2B&}Younger\NBrother
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:07.82,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\bord0.2\shad1\be1\fs28\4c&H4B4F3E&\c&H795764&\3c&H382B37&\frz44.41\frx356\fry332\pos(748,234)}Older\NBrother
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:12.61,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fnTimes New Roman\bord0.1\shad1.5\fs33\frx358\fry358\frz29.359\c&H363636&\pos(597,304)\3c&H4C4142&\4c&H928B8B&}The Fujiwara Brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:12.61,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H322F30&\shad0\bord2\be1\fs18\frz26.248\3c&H9C8A8D&\pos(722,390)\frx0\fry352}Older Bro./ Fujiwara Mario\NYounger Bro./ Fujiwara Luigi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:12.61,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\bord1\be1\shad0\fs20\pos(571,351)\frx348\fry6\frz30.629\c&H343231&\3c&H7A6E6E&}F.D.C. Fujiwara Design Office
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:12.61,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\c&H221C1A&\bord1.5\be1\shad0\fs24\b0\frz358.112\3c&HA9989B&\frx22\fry12\pos(274,344)}The Charismatic Sisters\Nof the World of Architecture!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:12.61,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\shad0\fs14\bord2\be1\c&HD5D4D4&\3c&H3B3B3B&\pos(187,104)\frz5.011\frx348\fry0}Youthful\NSibling\NUnit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:12.61,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\bord2\be1\shad0\fnArial\fscx80\fs20\c&H524D4E&\3c&HA8999C&\pos(112,265)\frz4.077\frx12\fry14}The Concept\Nis Brotherly Love
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:12.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Fujiwara Design has always\Nbeen famous for their family feuds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:16.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It becomes an issue when it gets this frequent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:20.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult, after all, to have two presidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:26.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although holding an office as a unit has become common\Nlately, I'm impressed when it actually lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But even when it's going well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:33.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are cases like Harada Design.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:38.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been four and a half years already\Nsince Harada-san left us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:41.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How fast time flies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:44.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They were a well-matched unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:51.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Together, Rika-san and her husband, Harada-san, would document\NRika-san's ideas as he implemented them with a smile on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a cool guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:12:02.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When he smiled and talked, it made\Nyou feel capable of doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:06.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone says that he was an amazing guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:10.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya and I were just running errands back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:13.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And we both admired him a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:20.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought from the bottom of my heart, "I want to\Nbe just like him when I become accomplished."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:26.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That no matter how difficult my task was, I would still\Ntackle it with a refreshing smile, like Harada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:30.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I think you've adopted that trait, Nomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:33.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya-san, it's done. May I have your signature?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:36.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya-san, I did it! I almost died, but\NI've got all the documents we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:38.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:42.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, I'm still far from Harada-san's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:47.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Harada-san was a truly amazing man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:54.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only person in this office who didn't\Nknow Harada-san when he was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel somewhat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:06.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:12.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that bowl that you made at\Nyour school for that one restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:16.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had other customers order that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:18.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They want "something similar".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:21.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's amazing, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:25.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, I had a friend of mine make that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:26.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I want to ask her to make as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:33.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you introduce me to this Yamada-san next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:34.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll have to talk to her about money...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:43.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the documents this time around are more\Ndetailed. I should talk to her in person...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be no problem as long as you give me a budget report.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:47.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave the rest up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:52.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's talk about future jobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:53.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:56.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a busy person, Nomiya-san. Please\Nconcentrate on your main task.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:14:01.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll really have no time to relax if you start working on pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:06.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you can give me all the documents,\NI'll discuss it with her tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're seeing her tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's part of my usual group of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Shinto shrine near my school that's holding a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:18.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make more coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:37.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Beef skewers! Okonomiyaki! Cotton candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I eat first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:44.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on a second! Calm down first! There's plenty of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:48.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to go get okonomiyaki\Nto suppress our hunger, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:51.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll calmly think it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:53.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us combined only have 3000 yen, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're causing such a ruckus...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:55.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all still kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:55.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Drinks are cheaper at the convenience store!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:58.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's times like this when I realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:02.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That it's good to be an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:04.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something I want to eat, I can eat it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:09.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have to have trouble deciding\Nor worrying about my wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:14.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I can't hit them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want the Whip-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:23.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The grand prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:24.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san, please get me one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it yourself if you're a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:34.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look! He got me a Whip-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:38.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:37.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stick to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:43.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you only doing it for Yamada-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:47.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, why do the youngsters make the old people feel so boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's a little difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:53.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Mayama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:55.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:56.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:57.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:16:00.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we figured we haven't been to a festival in too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:02.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:04.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(434,281)\c&H4C99D5&}"Festivals are nice, aren't they?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:07.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:10.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:15.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, why do you know my name...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Nomiya. It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for that bowl earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was well-received.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:22.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You really helped us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:23.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're from Mayama-kun's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:32.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As to be expected from Nomiya. He has good intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:37.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you were dissuading him so much, he figured\Nyou were definitely trying to hide something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you use such a dirty tactic, Yamada-san is really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:43.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You were hiding her from us, weren't you? I'm gonna strangle you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(434,236)\c&H4C99D5&}Festivals are fun, aren't they?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:53.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, his intuition is especially sharp\Nwhen it comes to things like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:55.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with just introducing them to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:57.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a cool-looking guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is that he's too cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:02.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that? She's awfully persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:03.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm at work right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:04.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A "self-proclaimed" girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:06.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya's never paying attention, so he\Ngets caught up in things like that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:06.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more important? Me or your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:08.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.30,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.4\be1\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\fs44\pos(232,85)\frz5.568\c&H69635A&\3c&H69635A&}Ehhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't litter in the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:18.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the kind of man who doesn't hesitate to throw a cell\Nphone filled with girl's numbers into the ocean at Shibaura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:20.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's certainly a big shot then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an act we couldn't perform even if our lives depended on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:27.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a big shot is too much for Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll eat her up in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:31.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll eat her whole from head to toe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Mayama... you're choking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:41.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... I'm fully aware that I'm in\Nno position to say things like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:46.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really want Yamada to have a happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:51.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want her getting used by guys who would\Napproach her with shallow intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:56.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me ask you this, what kind\Nof a guy wouldn't be too shallow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:57.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:06.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A person who's serious and tolerant with a steady income,\Nwho looks decent but would never cheat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:10.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A person who would treat her preciously for the\Nrest of her life and would never make her cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a mother with a teenage daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:18.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually think that such superficial data\Ncan guarantee a person's happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:28.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayama, if you can't be with her for every\Nfestival that will come up in her life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:32.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you certainly don't have the right\Nto interfere with her private life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:37.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:42.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That you can't worry about "what-ifs" when it comes to romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:44.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:49.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, I still wish that I could at least watch over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:56.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't say that even this feeling isn't just self-satisfaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:02.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:07.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you two here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was wondering why I hadn't\Nseen you two since this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:16.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we figured that we've both come to a point where we\Nneed to learn how to fill orders for potteries on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean you should come without asking me first...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem? If all of us work together, we'll finish sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:23.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do we need water?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I go fill that bucket?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is this the clay? I'll carry it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:36.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Those older guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:40.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you learn a little from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:43.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're just playing innocent, or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:47.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? It's rude of you\Nto talk about your seniors at work like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:48.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and put on an apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:56.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should tie your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:58.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a rubber band.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:03.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But shoot, my hands are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:06.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you put it on for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:12.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you butting in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What, am I bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:16.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:17.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you keep interfering...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:18.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:23.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:25.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess around next to the clay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:27.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If dust gets in, the clay will be ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:30.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down and knead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:31.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:33.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:36.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:43.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been punched by a woman since a\Nteacher scolded me in elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:48.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had it happen since my grandma back home hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot left to do, so let's all work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:54.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise we won't finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:59.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we finish, I'll deal with the mess, so\Nplease go home and rest, Nomiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:04.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I've been saying, why are you so desperate\Nto get rid of me, Mayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:07.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two! Quit moving your mouths and move your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Move over a little, Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not moving away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:11.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:14.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... Can't you listen to what your senior has to say to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:16.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In this case, I'll just pretend that I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:17.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
