Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:28.06,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}Taken advantage of by his smiling face
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:31.27,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kuchi ni shita sake ni aorarete, oh
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:31.27,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Stimulated by the alcohol she drank
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:34.23,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sora misereta toki ururunda face
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:34.23,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The tear that wells up when she's shown otherwise
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:37.95,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}ki ga sukkari sono ki ni natteru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:37.95,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}She'd already become all for it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:44.70,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}atama kakaete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:44.70,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}Holding her head
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:46.41,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(400,400)}atama kakaete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:46.41,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(400,400)}Holding her head
