Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:50.58,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}Even if she tries to pretend that it was a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:56.38,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}monogataru kare no paper
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:56.38,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}His paper tells a different story
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:22:01.97,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(400,400)}shiroku samete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:22:01.97,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(400,400)}Becoming white and discolored
